---
title: Teriyaki-Glazed Beef Meatballs with Sesame Rice, Pear Slaw & Peanuts
description: These meatballs are like nothing you’ve had before! The teriyaki glaze gives these morsels of deliciousness an amazing flavour
while the jasmine rice gets a hit of sesame. Just add a refreshing slaw with some extra crunch from pear to tie the meal together.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/teriyaki-glazed-beef-meatballs-0febbd74.jpg
